name: Hewlett Packard Enterprise
description: Hewlett Packard Enterprise Company provides solutions that allow customers to capture, analyze, and act upon data seamlessly in the Americas, Europe, the Middle East, Africa, the Asia Pacific, and Japan. It operates in five segments: Server, Hybrid Cloud, Intelligent Edge, Financial Services, and Corporate Investments and Other.
